snippet.title: Taxi Life: A City Driving Simulator | Pre-order Trailer
snippet.description:
After arriving in Barcelona with nothing but a car and a dream, drive around the busy streets of the famous city and transport passengers while offering them impeccable service. You will need to follow the rules of the road.

Taxi Life: A City Driving Simulator will be available on March 7th, 2024 on Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 5 and PC.

Pre-order Taxi Life: A City Driving Simulator and get your unique convertible Taxi! 

🚖 Playstation 👉 nacon.me/PreorderTaxiPS
🚖 Xbox 👉 nacon.me/PreorderTaxiXbox
🚖 Wishlist on Steam 👉 nacon.me/TaxiLifeSteam
